Fourth Minigame (Peter):
  The user has to shoot antidotes towards the viruses
  If a virus is shot, then it disappears 
  The user has to reach a score of 100 in order to beat the minigame
  
  Features:
    The user will shoot rays of antidotes similiar to asteroid smasher
    The user will be able to move and orient themselves around the screen
    The viruses will spawn randomly over the screen
    The viruses disappear when shot by an antidote
    The score will be trached at the top of the screen
